name: Dream Loving Fellas XI
description:
The Spiritual Heart is our ultimate and true nature, the ineffable dimension of our being. 
It constitutes the Ultimate Reality, transcendent and immanent in any aspect of the Macrocosm. It constitutes the ultimate essence of everything. It transcends duality.
Conceived as consciousness, the Heart is limitless.
It is the Infinite Light.

Dambass 2021
